A man in his 20s has died after being involved in a crash near Totnes.Devon and Cornwall Police said officers were called at about 19:00 BST on Monday to a country road near Washbourne to reports of a crash involving a Honda motorcycle and a white BMW X1.The force said the motorcycle rider, from Totnes, had since been pronounced dead. His next of kin have been informed.The road was closed whilst an investigation of the scene took place, and officers have asked for any witnesses or those with dashcam footage or information to come forward and assist its investigation.
